  "title" : "Clearing coverage highlighting in Eclipse",
  "body" : "<p>After running coverage reports in Eclipse (using cobertura or an EMMA plugin), my source code files get highlighted in green, red and yellow depending on which lines of code were covered by tests.</p>\n\n<p>How can I clear this highlighting after I'm done?</p>\n"
